<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font style="font-family: arial;"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="background-color: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span></span></font></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Your business insurance is now up for renewal with Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Have you considered adding&nbsp;<b>Cyber Liability</b>&nbsp;to your cover?<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Our Cyber Liability covers the cost of responding to a&nbsp;<b>cyber event&nbsp;</b>such as a&nbsp;<b>data breach</b>,&nbsp;<b>cyber attack</b>, or&nbsp;<b>ransomware incident</b>. Holding this type of cover can help to protect your business from the financial, operational, and reputational fallout of digital threats.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I’ve attached some information about our Cyber Liability cover in case you'd like to know more.<br></span><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Or if you'd prefer to talk through it in more detail, or would like to get it added to your renewal quote, please give me a call on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>.<br></font><span style="background-color: white;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font><font face="arial">Kind regards,<br></font></span><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-family: arial; background-color: white;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; background-color: white;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; background-color: white;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-family: arial; background-color: white;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: arial; background-color: white;">01242 808740</font></font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
